{"title":"Blubrake ABS G2 cuts bike antilock brake size & weight in half!","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/29/blubrake-abs-g2-cuts-bike-antilock-brake-size-weight-in-half/","date":1624971547000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>When Blubrake ABS debuted a bike anti-lock braking system, the size, weight &amp; internal mounting solution mostly limited its use to bigger cargo bikes &amp; bulky e-bikes. But now with the second generation, their ABS G2 is less than 1/2 the size, almost 1/2 the weight, and there’s a new fork mount option that simplifies installation and even allows ABS braking to be easily retrofitted onto existing bikes &amp; e-bikes…</p><h2>Blubrake ABS G2 is a smaller, lighter bike anti-lock braking system</h2><p><span><iframe width=\"696\" height=\"392\" data-ezsrc=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/ljC_nXovZiA?version=3&amp;rel=1&amp;showsearch=0&amp;showinfo=1&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;fs=1&amp;hl=en-US&amp;autohide=2&amp;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation\" ezoid=\"0.9227984185520828\"></iframe></span></p><p>The concept remains the same as in <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2021/04/23/blubrake-creates-electronic-abs-for-e-bikes-ruins-those-crazy-cargo-bike-front-skids/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">its first generation</a>, Blubrake ABS G2 is an active anti-lock braking system tailored for bikes, and specifically e-bikes, that processes speed sensor &amp; accelerometer data to prevent front brake lock-ups.</p><figure id=\"attachment_263308\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-263308\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount.jpg\" alt=\"Blubrake ABS G2 bicycle anti-lock braking system, smaller lighter bike antilock brakes,&nbsp;city cruising\" width=\"1200\" height=\"900\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-265x198.jpg 265w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-297x223.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-800x600.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-120x90.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-768x576.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-696x522.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-1068x801.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-560x420.jpg 560w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-80x60.jpg 80w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085020/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_city-fork-mount-265x198.jpg 265w\"></a><figcaption id=\"caption-attachment-263308\">all photos c. Blubrake</figcaption></figure><p>This still isn’t quite a lightweight ABS system that is likely to pop up on more conventional bikes – it still requires a relatively bulky system and an external power source, typically from an e-bike battery – but it is true, full power anti-lock braking, unlike for example the lighter, simpler <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/?s=outbraker\">Outbraker</a> which simply modulates max brake power to prevent skidding. And for the heavier weight of e-bikes, managing those heavier e-bikes over loose surfaces, and especially for less experienced riders, Blubrake ABS G2 should deliver more control and safer full-power braking.</p><h3>Tech details – What’s new?</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com