ntilock-brakes_inside-700x420.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1500px) 100vw, 1500px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb20 src ng ngcb20 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside.jpg 1500w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-297x178.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-800x480.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-120x72.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-768x461.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-696x418.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-1068x641.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085013/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_inside-700x420.jpg 700w\"></a></p><p>Gen2 is simply 65% smaller and 47% lighter, down to 380g, thanks to revised system design that integrates the electronic controller &amp; hydraulic brake actuator into one unit. Now, it can more easily fit inside frames for a fully integrated setup, or a new fork mount allows it to be retrofitted onto existing e-bikes without altering the frame.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components.jpg\" alt=\"Blubrake ABS G2 bicycle anti-lock braking system, smaller lighter bike antilock brakes,&nbsp;system diagram\" width=\"2000\" height=\"750\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components.jpg 2000w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components-297x111.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components-800x300.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lock-braking-system_smaller-lighter-bike-antilock-brakes_components-120x45.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/29085006/Blubrake-ABS-G2-bicycle-anti-lo